    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the <strong>Hacker</strong>, trapped in the virtual dome known as <strong>Sector 598</strong> being lead and controlled by the ADMIN for the past 28 years. Things change once the <strong>Hacker</strong> finds out there is something sinister going on, can you fight your way out and escape in this turn based strategy game?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296080/extras/e4d16575a87a085b4861a1e7bf15eaf3.poster.avif?t=1730251441\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296080/extras/e4d16575a87a085b4861a1e7bf15eaf3.webm?t=1730251441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296080/extras/e4d16575a87a085b4861a1e7bf15eaf3.mp4?t=1730251441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Unique maps and levels. In this 3-5 hour story with 3 endings and 20 unique maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create new allies by finding hidden collectibles. You will need all the help you get to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mystery of Sector 598. Only those who dare to escape will uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you dare to escape?</p>",
